            <Text>Eelan Toon
West of the Ring, south of Oknott, east of The Weir Lands

Role in Story
Eelan is the name both of a province within the Borded Federation and the main town in the province.

Provide some sense of the older inhabitants of the region, who are neither Fatunik, nor devotees of the southern beliefs, nor Kahila, nor part of the new/high/hidden thinking found in places like the Empafarasi Weir Lands and parts of the Outer Lands. 

The mines and hills of Eelan to provide the material foundation of the musical character of the region, and the character of its people.  These are country/hill people, hard working miners, not easily impressed, determinedly fond of their folkways which tend towards an affinity for the Finders.

Duty. Tradition
