Type of Location
A province of the Fatunika located within the Great Ring Road, bordering the Bordeddi province of Eelan to the west.
The main towns in the province are Bordakol and Heliohlan.
There are also two important military bases in the province, reflecting the old conflicts with the westerners, particularly the Eelani.  The Borda Woods sees itself as the the Protector of the Center. This is where Tonedo Remper is from.
