Role in Story
Let's re-purpose this character. OK if I still want him to originate from Arq and have a canine blend, but he needs to be Eelani through and through. A leader, a known character in Eelan Town. Perhaps an empresario of sorts. 

The Eelani are not a tribal clan in the usual sense, like in Mobalbes, the Nye Lands and Byenung. They are diverse mountain people who came to hills to work in the mines from all parts of the Saskan Lands. This created an open, egalitarian society with few centralized authorities. The mines are run by the syndicates (guilds) of workers who work in them, with profits shared out according to seniority and difficulty of tasks. More cooperative than many of the other guilds, and run democratically.

