Injecting yet another level of complexity into the overall orchestration, Jesse K is a rebel from the Agency, a fallen angel as it were. She wants to blow open the uselessness of the Agency and expose their lack of direction, failure to succeed in their mission.  But has little if anything in the way of an explanation either for their action or her own. Likes to stir things up just to see what will happen.

