            <Title>Ch 22 - Summary 02</Title>
            <Text>A Mobalbesqan naval flotilla that includes our intrepid voyagers returning from Wing Island stops at the Setta Delta to pick up advisors from The Runes of Bye, then at Selaron to drop off supplies for the defense of Ríkila, along with other trade goods. 

