Iohane's Calvary.
Humor

MM's comment on Tonedo should be along the lines of: "This man may look like an idiot and act like an idiot, but don't be fooled. He really is an idiot."
Truth

Living things do not actually "grow" in the sense of a given thing -- a molecule let's say -- getting bigger. That is a kind of illusion. Yes, bones "grow" and flesh "grows" but the underlying reality is that living cells are multiplying and becoming increasingly interactive, tied together in increasingly complex ways through myriad chemical and physical chains of reactions. 
