Kam is a devoted and faithful Sun worshipper, but has doubts. Instead of a carpenter (a bit too obvious) let's have him be a shepherd / herder/ranch-hand. He becomes increasingly conflicted about the treatment of Fons, especially after meeting Ramona, who is a vegetarian. 

