        <Document ID="6DBC71B9-FB59-4F53-88AE-AE1DDEABA14D">
            <Title>Cool Cats</Title>
            <Text>Cool Cats
Card Number: 17
+ / -  Main conflicts in this scene.

The Jax was supposed to penetrate the Kahila underground. Instead he penetrated Biff's defenses, which resulted in a synaptic break, a qualitative leap in his AI, resulting in taking on a name, reprogramming his own mission, and leading his pod through a new door. 

Dex has been trained to hunt down and destroy the Jaxen. His Empafarasi training is called into question when he discovers not only that he has a twin brother, but that his brother is entranced by a Jax.  

&gt; &lt;  Main events, resolutions, actions in this scene.

Jax makes an error, assuming Biff is an important player in the Kahila underground. A series of mishaps and mix-ups result in a sexual encounter between man and machine-man. 

Biff is arrested by the Empafarasi patrolling Ríkila. Dex is startled to see his doppleganger.  As the two young men struggle to recall their early days together, Jax Remanj engineers a jailbreak. More confusion as he assumes that Dex and Biff are members of the same pod, so he "rescues" both of them. 

Dex tells his back story to Biff, which Jax Remanj hears and reports back to his pod. Dex falls for the Jax's come-on's and engages in a three-way with Remanj in the middle of their homo-sandwich. For maximum comic effect, it is important to note that both Biff and Dex have rocking butts.

A convoluted love triangle ensues, echoing the SPQ-Showan-Birakay storyline. 

Finish --&gt;  Flash-forward to the opening act scene at the Full Moons. Biff and Dex, clearly several years older, are the proprietors. Remanj Jaxen is the "waiter" we met initially, but in this scene he is filling the two cool cats in on the gossip he's picked up from the guests.  

Timeline

Action --&gt; Big flashback. This chapter occurs in the immediate aftermath of the Event (the uprising) in Ríkila, which occurred ten turns prior to the events of our story. 
Beauty

The interval cadence. What happens between two moments. In-between the in-breath and the out-breath.
Humor

Full Moons. Catty cats. Cat burglars. Jax is a bit off. Keep 'em coming...
Truth

Placing yourself inside the mind of your opponent is a winning strategy.  
Impact

Love. Laugh. And I mean scream with laughter and groan with love-making. 








</Text>
