            <Title>Dex and Biff</Title>
            <Text>Dex and Biff
19 • High Weir, Ríkila

Role in Story
Always nice to have some kind of twisty twins tale to play around with... in this case, it helps to tell the "tale of two cities" with respect to Ríkila -- that den of popular uprisings and conspiracies -- and High Weir -- those virtuous Empafarasi who fancy themselves the true elite of the Saskan Lands.  

Goal
Through their strange entanglement, reveal something of the east-west dialectic to this story, with a potential for synthesis when the two of them finally meet, work thru their personal anger and conflicts, to maybe find some kind of approach to not only settling the old mis-perceptions, but finding a way to merge the Old Rebellion and the New Way... 

Physical Description
Twin boybeks, but unknown to each other, having been separated at a young age. 

Personality
Dex is a member of a Empafarasi unit responsible mainly for patrolling the hills to insure villagers are safe from wild Fons (meaning non-sentient animals, wild animals) and on the lookout for incursions from the Krunkinotto.  He seeks glory and is known as kind of a shit-head. He is strong and quick, to his credit, but without a lot of fortitude.  Good in an encounter, but not on a long march.  Despite his tendency to tire out fairly quickly, he has a strong constitution and tends to heal quickly when hurt.

He's never been examined and claims to be 100% bek, but is sometimes (usually jokingly) called "Dex the Cat" etc. by his comrades.  His foresight and perception are sharp. He has slight powers of heightened hearing and seeing, with a mild ability to foresee possibilities clearly -- although he doesn't himself realize these are enhanced powers.  

His twin brother, called Biff, is similar in all ways, but has lived most of his life in Ríkila, falling in with a number of bitamin outfits there and making a living mostly as a very successful cat-burgler, and running a number of confidence schemes as well. 


Occupation


Habits/Mannerisms


Background
During the initial Empafarasi interventions in Ríkila, Dex was sent with an advanced team to scope things out. They arrived in an official capacity to parlay with the various factions and thus were quite visible to watching eyes of all types.  Biff picked up on their similar appearance and used this as a means to carry out various cons.  Following complaints from locals, Biff was eventually apprehended by Empafarasi agents and taken to High Weir under guard for judgement by the highland court.  That was how Dex and Biff are re-united.

