            <Text>The Splendid Boys


Card 9a

This chapter focuses on Showan and Birakay. And through them, flashbacks to Quinn's background and childhood.


As our team travels the seaways and roads to Byenung and Wye, rumors swirl about events at the Authority, the Byenung intellectual-legal community is an uproar over the arrest of Quinn, Henqu and Iohane, and the Mobal Beshqi mobilize their own Argumentation team to defend the New Science. 

