Birakay, through ongoing performances and interactions with fans thorughout the Outer Lands, foreshadows stories that will be wrapping up or presented as cliff-hangers in chapter 10 of Act One. 


These tales reveal aspects of the archetypal selves of Showan, Birakay and Stanley:
- The mask - how they present themselves to the world
- The shadow - their sexual and other instincts
- The anima - the feminine aspects of their character
