            <Text>Scatterling
A village in the province of Terpinol

Role in Story
A place where the Green, a philosophical school originated at the Academy in Terpinol, has a center and where various factions and incarnations of the Mages Guild gather from time to time.

Related Characters
Guilds who maintain their leadership councils in the village are the Free and Independent Tailors, the Free and Independent Scribes Guild, and the Independent Healers Association.

The Dauni Valasaqa also keep a permanent representative in Scatterling. 

Season


Unique Features
Produces unique clothing known for its style and durability. 
The Dauni Vakasaqua and healers of Scatterling are known for having cures that actually work against deadly diseases and infections. Continuing the theme of the façades of the place, they front for one of the few active medical clinics, including surgeries, in the region.  

