            <Title>Sleeths</Title>
            <Text>Sleeths
Age • Location

Role in Story
Interest, background

Goal


Physical Description
One of the few highly-sentient mixed-with-huum actors with a distinctly non-huum appearance.  Sleeths are reptilian -- a joke on the whole reptile aliens from .. whatever thing.  Except in this case, they are actually descended from those alien-reptilian predecessors who arrived from a star system in the direction of Draco long, long, long ago. 

But are not evil or dangerous at all. Just the opposite. 

They look very much like huge lizards, but with hands, feet, semi-huum-looking heads.

They have a very distinctive Bar dialect -- Sleebar -- that is difficult for most Sogomsh and Eibar speakers to grasp, yet is not an Eibarq or Arqq variety. 
Personality
Unlike their ancestors, tho, and despite their bizarre appearance, Sleeths are pacifist, pastoral, anarchic in their approach to governance. They are the Jains -- or at least the Sikhs -- of the Saskan Lands


