Concerns about sins of the fathers.   Sleeth children are taught to never mix with huum and to never, never try to pretend they are huum.   They blame their ancestors for many of the worst atrocities in huum history, possibly for the Catastrophe itself.

External Conflicts
Considered unclean by many Heliops, the Sleeth clans are subject to cruel treatment by the more extreme elements of the Tagabant. Even Rider-affiliated and Eelani huum tend to recoil the first time they encounter Sleeths, thinking they are dangerous like Arns or Jacks. 

