Syncronicity. South meets North in western context on the Ring outside Eelan.

Petra Bearbek leaves her enclave in the Kahila Woods to engage the Dauni Vakasaqua in the developing uprising, by bringing Malavorra out onto the Ring Road. This creates a sensation through the Settan Lands. They offer protection to Allane and Kaharan, to the consternation of the DV elders who oppose fomenting any conflicts with the Heliops.

&gt; &lt;  Main events, resolutions, actions in this scene.

