The busy-body-ness of Byenung betrays the beaverific nature of its boroughs. 
Truth

One shouldn't run away from a true ruler. 
Impact

It would be a great torment for any of the boys to lay aside the one they care for the most. Yet each of them must do so in order to complete their journey.




